{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"329056314f","title":"女工和农妇们，要记住并实现伊里奇的遗训！","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"dc5b87329b","index":0,"year":1925,"month":1,"day":5,"articleId":"329056314f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","name":"斯大林选集（诸夏怀斯社2017年5月）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"斯大林，诸夏怀斯社2017年5月","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1332d101b8","name":"斯大林"}]},"publication_details":{"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5b46483a7f","type":"paragraph","text":"女工和农妇们","index":0,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f"},{"id":"02291a19ba","type":"paragraph","text":"要记存并实现伊里奇的遗训！","index":1,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f"},{"id":"009e6c97a5","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九二五年一月五日）","index":2,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f"},{"id":"3636af2e24","type":"paragraph","text":"一年前，劳动人民的伟大领袖和导师，我们的列宁，在和我们永别的时候给我们留下了遗训，指出了我们走向共产主义最后胜利所应遵循的道路。女工和农妇们，你们要实现伊里奇的这些遗训！你们要用这些遗训的精神去教育你们的孩子！","index":3,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f"},{"id":"794445a42e","type":"paragraph","text":"列宁同志临终时骗附我们要竭力巩固工农联盟。女工和农妇们你们要巩固这个联盟！","index":4,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f"},{"id":"eb999459c1","type":"paragraph","text":"列宁同志教导劳动人民要支持工人阶级去反对国内外的资产阶级女工和农妇们，你们要记住这个遗训，你们要支持正在建设新生活的工人阶级的政权！","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f"},{"id":"8969cabbeb","type":"paragraph","text":"列宁同志教导我们要高举起一切被压道者的领袖—一共产党的旗积。女工和农妇们，你们要团结在这个党的周围，——它是你们的党！","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f"},{"id":"f5561ad1bf","type":"paragraph","text":"值此伊里奇进世一周年纪念之际，党号召：要为女工和农妇们为止在和党一起建设新生活的女工和农妇们开解更厂阔的道路。","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f"},{"id":"473c82aeac","type":"paragraph","text":"约·斯大林写于一九二五年一月五日","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f"},{"id":"6ed59ef2cf","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集》","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f"},{"id":"6105950074","type":"paragraph","text":"第7卷第3页载于一九二五年一月“女工”杂志第一期","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f"}],"page":{"id":"310e16e8f0","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"329056314f","start":784,"end":784}}}},"__N_SSG":true}